===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[paleolithicus]]'' from Gk ''[[palaios]]'' old and ''[[lithos]]'' stone + ''[[-ikos]]''

===Noun===
'''palaeolithic'''
# A period that lasted from two million years ago to 10,000 [[BC]], of or relating to the [[Old Stone Age]].

